(ados-27/) Tj
T*
(Apple Newsroom, in an Apple Newsroom post Monday: According to EU regulators, the DMA requires) Tj
T*
(Apple to give any AI system nearly unlimited access to a user?s device, as well as the ability) Tj
T*
(to act on that access autonomously without a user?s ongoing visibility and control. That) Tj
T*
(includes the ability to read and send messages, make purchases, access files, and execute) Tj
T*
(actions across any app. Security researchers have already shown that AI systems can be hijacked) Tj
T*
(to steal personal data ? like passwords and photos ? and to permanently alter files and account) Tj
T*
(settings without a user?s consent. As AI systems gain more capabilities, these risks are) Tj
T*
(quickly increasing in frequency and scope. Given the serious risks to users, Apple designed a) Tj
T*
(solution called Trusted System Agent ? an intermediary that would allow virtual assistants to) Tj
T*
(safely access the same features and capabilities as Siri AI for devices in the EU. Apple also) Tj
